   <dc:title>Handwritten postcard from Dahms to Schenker, dated November 13, 1926</dc:title>

   <dcterms:created>1926-11-13T12:00:00Z</dcterms:created>
   <dcterms:dateSubmitted>2012-03-27</dcterms:dateSubmitted>
   <dc:description>Dahms has written his review of Meisterwerk, and has dispatched a copy of his
    Almanach to Schenker. </dc:description>
   <dc:subject>Musikfreunde; music lovers; Prospektus; prospectus; Schülern; pupils; students </dc:subject>

   
   
